PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773936670
OL,3,CBank keeps interest rates on hold and
OL,4,Cwarns the war will push up inflation
OL,6,F"The most exciting 'Hold' in history,"
OL,7,Fdeclared the journalist sitting next
OL,8,Fto me. Indeed.
OL,10,FThe Monetary Policy Committee at the
OL,11,FBank of England has voted unanimously
OL,12,Fto keep interest rates at 3.75% -
OL,13,Fwarning that the war in the Gulf is
OL,14,Fputting upward pressure on prices
OL,15,Facross the UK.
OL,17,FNot so long ago, everyone in the City
OL,18,Fhad a cut penciled in.
OL,20,FWar has changed everything.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
